=== Ps Puffar ===
Contributors: dinwebb, spathon
Tags: puffar, widget
Requires at least: 3.0
Tested up to: 3.1
Stable tag: 0.7


== Description ==

Ps Puffar is a plugin to make it easy to insert custom text/forms images and more on unique pages.

The plugin started as an fast and easy way to add puffar on small sites. It is in need for a better connection between page an puff for use on big sites.

<a href="http://labs.dinwebb.nu/plugins/ps-puffar/">Read more</a>

= Translations =

Languages:
* English

Don't see your language on the list? Feel free to translate.


== Installation ==

* Download the files
* Upload the files to wp-content/plugins/
* Activate the plugin
* Go to Puffar -> settings in the admin menu and select the post types you want to use puffar on
* Now it√≠s just start creating Puffar



